========================================================================
WHAT THIS BRANCH DOES
========================================================================

Adds online horizontal remapping, vertical coarsening, derived field
computation, and vertical reduction to E3SM for FME (Full Model
Emulation) training data generation (ACE/Samudra). Eliminates offline
postprocessing for FME training data.

Overhead: +1.6% wallclock (7.56 s on 485 s baseline, 512 tasks).

Key source files:
  share/util/shr_horiz_remap_mod.F90    -- CRS SpMV remap + apply_masked
  share/util/shr_vcoarsen_mod.F90       -- vertical coarsening math
  share/util/shr_derived_mod.F90        -- expression parser (TOTAL_WATER)
  components/eam/src/control/           -- EAM wrappers (horiz_remap,
                                           vcoarsen, derived, tendencies)
  components/mpas-ocean/src/            -- 3 AMs + horiz_remap wrapper
  components/mpas-seaice/src/           -- 1 AM + horiz_remap wrapper
